configparam.description:
Specifies analytic routings in the QR. When a request matching an analytic is found, the request can be routed to multiple databases.
Two modes - static & dynamic
Static: if 'targets' field is populated, static list of connection groups, connections and/or instances can be configured for the routing Dynamic: otherwise category, class, subClass, tag1 & tag2 values can be matched to dynamic database coverage information. See Query Router documentation for more information on registering coverage.
aggFunction - used to specify a custom collection analytic for analytic. Analytic should have a valence of 1
